            <title><![CDATA[Battlefield 6 Dev Wishes Secure Boot Wasn't Needed--"I Wish Everyone Could Play"]]></title>
            <link>https://www.gamespot.com/articles/battlefield-6-dev-wishes-secure-boot-wasnt-needed-i-wish-everyone-could-play/1100-6534357/?ftag=CAD-01-10abi2f</link>
